    "The girl following behind asked as if curious."

# game/chapter7.rpy:357
translate english chapter7_f8b2ab9f:

    # "소녀의 목소리에는 티 나지 않을 정도의 기대감이 섞여 있었다. "
    "There was a hint of anticipation in the girl's voice that was barely noticeable."

# game/chapter7.rpy:359
translate english chapter7_2edcd69a:

    # "나는 침을 꿀꺽 삼키고는, 최대한 소녀의 기대감을 고통 없이 죽일 수 있을 법한 목소리로 내 계획을 요약했다. "
    "I swallowed my saliva and summarized my plan in a voice that could kill the girl's anticipation without pain as much as possible."

# game/chapter7.rpy:361
translate english chapter7_09193db8:

    # 나 "“…… 그날의 일을 재현하는 거야.”"
    나 "\"... We're going to recreate that day.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:363
translate english chapter7_044aa059:

    # "소녀가 그 문장을 이해하는 데까지는 그리 오랜 시간이 걸리지 않았다. "
    "It didn't take long for the girl to understand that sentence."

# game/chapter7.rpy:367
translate english chapter7_a680ceaa:

    # voice "voices/gg24.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 네에?”"
    voice "voices/gg24.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... Huh?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:369
translate english chapter7_768acefb:

    # voice ""
    # "나를 뒤따라오던 소녀는, 나의 앞을 가로막아 섰다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl following me stood in my way."

# game/chapter7.rpy:372
translate english chapter7_4f607078:

    # 나 "“정확하게는…… 내 몸에 좀 충격을 줘 보면 목소리가 들려오지 않을까 해서. 물론 옥상에서 떨어지는 건 좀 무리가 있을 테니까, 3층이나 2층 정도에서 뛰어내려 보면…….”"
    나 "\"To be precise... I thought if I gave my body a bit of a shock, maybe the voice would come back. Of course, jumping off the rooftop might be a bit too much, so maybe jumping from the 3rd or 2nd floor...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:374
translate english chapter7_2115c35f:

    # voice "voices/gg25.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“말도 안 되는 소리 하지 마세요.”"
    voice "voices/gg25.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Don't say such nonsense.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:379
translate english chapter7_0ba933f3:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 가로막은 길을 비켜 줄 생각이 전혀 없어 보였다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl seemed to have no intention of stepping aside."

# game/chapter7.rpy:381
translate english chapter7_f20781c5:

    # "서로의 마주한 시선이 그대로 굳어버린 채 시간이 흐른다. "
    "Time passed as our gazes locked in place."

# game/chapter7.rpy:382
translate english chapter7_7784908a:

    # "한숨을 크게 내쉰 소녀가, 내 쪽으로 걸어오며 먼저 입을 열었다. "
    "The girl let out a big sigh and walked towards me, opening her mouth first."

# game/chapter7.rpy:388
translate english chapter7_f63d2086:

    # voice "voices/gg26.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그때의 일을 재현하려는 거죠?”"
    voice "voices/gg26.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You're trying to recreate what happened then?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:390
translate english chapter7_d5d59314:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“최대한 비슷하게 만들어 보려는 거지. 그렇게 위험한 일은 아니라니까?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I'm trying to replicate it as closely as possible. It's not that dangerous, okay?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:393
translate english chapter7_75834a3f:

    # voice "voices/gg27.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“굳이 그러려고 한다면, 제가 떨어지는 걸 받아 주면 되잖아요.”"
    voice "voices/gg27.ogg"
    소녀 "\"If you're really going to do that, I could catch you when you fall.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:395
translate english chapter7_6467217e:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“네가 떨어지겠다고?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"You're going to catch me?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:398
translate english chapter7_a8023286:

    # "소녀와의 대화는 생각했던 것과 다른 방향으로 흘러가고 있었다. "
    "The conversation with the girl was taking a different turn than I had expected."

# game/chapter7.rpy:400
translate english chapter7_6c947aee:

    # voice "voices/gg28.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“일단 저는 유령이니까…… 잘못될 일은 없는걸요. 그리고 그때의 일을 재현하려는 거라면서요? 그럼 최대한 비슷한 상황을 만들어야죠.”"
    voice "voices/gg28.ogg"
    소녀 "\"First of all, I'm a ghost... so nothing can go wrong. And you said you want to recreate what happened then? Then we have to create a situation as similar as possible.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:402
translate english chapter7_a82ab6ae:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그러다 잘못 떨어지면 어떡하려고?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"What if you fall wrong?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:405
translate english chapter7_857d6e94:

    # voice "voices/gg29.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“조금 아프고 말 뿐이에요. 오히려 그쪽이 떨어지는 게 더 위험할 거라고요.”"
    voice "voices/gg29.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It'll just hurt a bit. In fact, it would be more dangerous for you to fall.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:407
translate english chapter7_519af0eb:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 확실해?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... Are you sure?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:410
translate english chapter7_c3f10c13:

    # voice "voices/gg30.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“확실해요. 해 봤으니까요. 여러 번.”"
    voice "voices/gg30.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I'm sure. Because I've done it. Several times.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:412
translate english chapter7_dfa08553:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 그렇지만.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... Even so.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:415
translate english chapter7_ce8de7db:

    # voice "voices/gg31.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“사실 위험한 일이었다고 하면 화낼 거예요.”"
    voice "voices/gg31.ogg"
    소녀 "\"If it were really dangerous, I'd be angry.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:417
translate english chapter7_34ddd110:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 후우, 알겠어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... Phew, okay.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:427
translate english chapter7_50d3fa63:

    # "소녀의 모든 부분이, 이번만큼은 내가 그녀를 설득시킬 수 없으리라는 것을 분명히 알려주고 있었다. "
    "Every part of the girl was clearly telling me that this time, I wouldn't be able to persuade her."

# game/chapter7.rpy:428
translate english chapter7_31ceb234:

    # "이번엔 내가 한숨을 내쉴 차례인 모양이었다. "
    "It seemed to be my turn to sigh this time."

# game/chapter7.rpy:433
translate english chapter7_3110ecb5:

    # "폐전신국 안쪽으로 발걸음을 옮기는 소녀. "
    "The girl moved her steps into the abandoned telegraph station."

# game/chapter7.rpy:434
translate english chapter7_7aa13a49:

    # "나는 그런 소녀를 멍하니 바라볼 뿐이었다. "
    "I could only stare blankly at her doing so."

# game/chapter7.rpy:442
translate english chapter7_fadc71ae:

    # "얼마 지나지 않아 모습을 드러낸 소녀가 내게 손을 흔들어 보이며 위치를 알렸다. "
    "The girl, who had appeared not long after, waved to me, indicating her position."

# game/chapter7.rpy:443
translate english chapter7_3a42312f:

    # "소녀가 모습을 드러낸 곳은 폐전신국 3층의 깨진 유리창 너머였다. "
    "The place where the girl had appeared was beyond the broken window of the third floor of the abandoned telegraph station."

# game/chapter7.rpy:445
translate english chapter7_0ad6ff97:

    # voice "voices/gg32.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“지금 뛰어내리면 될까요?!”"
    voice "voices/gg32.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Should I jump now?!\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:447
translate english chapter7_08a88a0e:

    # voice ""
    # "마른 침을 삼키고, OK 사인을 건넸다. "
    voice ""
    "I swallowed my dry saliva and gave her an OK sign."

# game/chapter7.rpy:449
translate english chapter7_7f800265:

    # "조금씩, 심장박동이 빨라지는 것이 느껴졌다. "
    "Little by little, I could feel my heartbeat quickening."

# game/chapter7.rpy:451
translate english chapter7_46e2d33d:

    # voice "voices/gg33.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“저…… 잘 받아 줘야 해요?!”"
    voice "voices/gg33.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You... have to catch me properly?!\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:453
translate english chapter7_b6ebfecf:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“알겠어―――”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Got it―――\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:456
translate english chapter7_6c6253a3:

    # "숨을 고르며 머릿속에 현지를 받아냈을 때의 상황을 그린다. "
    "Taking a deep breath, I pictured in my mind the situation when I caught Hyeonji."

# game/chapter7.rpy:457
translate english chapter7_3d8645df:

    # "그때처럼, 별일 없을 것이다. "
    "Just like then, nothing will happen."

# game/chapter7.rpy:458
translate english chapter7_73cd3439:

    # "다만 나를 부르는 목소리가 들려오고, 그 목소리가 소녀와 이어지기만을 기다리면 되는 것이다. "
    "Only the voice calling me is heard, and all I have to do is wait for that voice to connect with the girl."

# game/chapter7.rpy:462
translate english chapter7_455c64fe:

    # "머릿속을 장밋빛 예감으로 가득 채우고는, 떨어지는 소녀를 받아낼 준비를 한다. "
    "Filling my mind with rosy anticipation, I prepare to catch the falling girl."

# game/chapter7.rpy:466
translate english chapter7_433b7366:

    # "소녀가 떨어지고, 나는 소녀를 향해 손을 뻗었다. "
    "The girl fell and I reached out towards her."

# game/chapter7.rpy:474
translate english chapter7_8d5771bd:

    # "눈을 뜨자, 나의 품속에 안긴 소녀가 보인다. "
    "As I opened my eyes, I saw the girl nestled in my arms."

# game/chapter7.rpy:475
translate english chapter7_88243e40:

    # "걱정은 마치 기우였다는 듯, 공주님처럼 내게 안긴 소녀가 조금은 부끄러운 듯 얼굴을 붉힌다. "
    "As if all the worry was for naught, the girl snuggled up to me like a princess, her face reddening slightly as if embarrassed."

# game/chapter7.rpy:476
translate english chapter7_dd8a5812:

    # "하지만 소녀는 그 자세가 마음에 들었는지, 그대로 눈을 감고선 자신에게 이어질 목소리를 가만히 기다린다. "
    "But the girl seemed to like this position, she closed her eyes and quietly waited for the voice that would connect to her."

# game/chapter7.rpy:477
translate english chapter7_413f3eb5:

    # "그러자 익숙한 목소리가 나를 부르고, 담쟁이덩굴처럼 뻗어 나온 운명의 실이 소녀와 이어진다. "
    "Then a familiar voice called me, and the thread of fate, stretching out like ivy, connected with the girl."

# game/chapter7.rpy:478
translate english chapter7_42274373:

    # "더할 나위 없이 행복한 자세로, 소녀는 행복한 기억을 되찾아가는지 입가에 편안한 미소를 띤다. "
    "In an utterly blissful posture, the girl regained her happy memories and wore a comfortable smile on her lips."

# game/chapter7.rpy:479
translate english chapter7_3b8a6d4d:

    # "모두가 행복한 결말을 향해, 한 발짝 다가가는 것이다. "
    "Everyone is taking a step towards a happy ending."

# game/chapter7.rpy:481
translate english chapter7_b1b876ac:

    # "―――그랬으면 좋겠다고, 눈을 뜨기 전까지 생각했다. "
    "That's what I thought until I opened my eyes―――"

# game/chapter7.rpy:485
translate english chapter7_d345a417:

    # "눈을 떴을 때, 주변은 침묵의 원색으로 물들어 있었다. "
    "When I opened my eyes, the surroundings were dyed in the primary color of silence."

# game/chapter7.rpy:486
translate english chapter7_c86837cb:

    # "아무것도 들려오지 않았다. "
    "I couldn't hear anything."

# game/chapter7.rpy:487
translate english chapter7_2a5879b2:

    # "소녀와 나의 이어짐을 의미하는 목소리는커녕, 그녀의 존재를 의미하던 자그마한 소리조차도. "
    "Not only the voice that signified the connection between the girl and me but even the slightest sound that meant her existence."

# game/chapter7.rpy:488
translate english chapter7_a998ce67:

    # "아무것도 느껴지지 않았다. "
    "I couldn't feel anything."

# game/chapter7.rpy:490
translate english chapter7_32a9e8d9:

    # "황급히 주위를 돌아보았지만, 주변은 원래 그랬다는 것처럼 아무도 보이지 않았다. "
    "I hurriedly looked around but saw no one as if it had always been that way."

# game/chapter7.rpy:491
translate english chapter7_259bfee1:

    # "침이 잘 삼켜지지 않았다. "
    "I found it hard to swallow my saliva."

# game/chapter7.rpy:492
translate english chapter7_ebd43886:

    # "온몸을 지탱하고 있던 무언가가 스르르 빠져나가는 듯한 기분이 들었다. "
    "I felt as if something that had been supporting my body was slowly draining away."

# game/chapter7.rpy:493
translate english chapter7_1a734dc3:

    # "허공을 붙잡고 있던 손이 제자리를 찾았다. "
    "My hand, which had been clutching at thin air, found its place again."

# game/chapter7.rpy:498
translate english chapter7_94369701:

    # "소녀가 사라졌다. "
    "The girl disappeared."

# game/chapter7.rpy:499
translate english chapter7_738565eb:

    # "허무하리만치 쉽게, 소녀는 내 눈앞에서 사라졌다. "
    "With an emptiness too great to bear, the girl vanished before my eyes."

# game/chapter7.rpy:500
translate english chapter7_79113c72:

    # "그토록 바랐던 결말이 이런 형태로 다가올 거라곤 생각조차 못 했는데. "
    "I hadn't even considered that the ending I so desired would come in this form."

# game/chapter7.rpy:504
translate english chapter7_cde2a7b2:

    # "소녀는 애초에 존재하지 않았던 것처럼, 일말의 잔향조차 남기지 않은 채 사라져버린 뒤였다. "
    "The girl disappeared without leaving a trace, as if she had never existed in the first place."

# game/chapter7.rpy:505
translate english chapter7_e41cd437:

    # "나와 부딪힐 때의 충격이 소녀를 사라지게 만든 것이라 짐작하는 수밖엔, 달리 방법이 없었다. "
    "I had no other choice but to guess that the shock of our collision made the girl disappear."

# game/chapter7.rpy:507
translate english chapter7_f61f5075:

    # 나 "“…… 그렇구나.”"
    나 "\"... I see.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:509
translate english chapter7_6871a06d:

    # "어쨌거나 소녀가 사라지게 되었다면, 이걸로 된 걸까. "
    "Anyway, if the girl has disappeared, is this considered settled?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:516
translate english chapter7_48bf2ee7:

    # "들려오길 바랐던 형태 없는 목소리 대신, 어지럼증을 동반한 이명이 뇌리를 스친다. "
    "Instead of the formless voice I hoped to hear, a dizzying tinnitus sweeps through my brain."

# game/chapter7.rpy:517
translate english chapter7_e65674ea:

    # "미간이 찌푸려질 정도로 눈을 감았다. "
    "I closed my eyes tightly enough to furrow my brows."

# game/chapter7.rpy:524
translate english chapter7_ed5b66d5:

    # voice "voices/gg34.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“―――괜찮아요?”"
    voice "voices/gg34.ogg"
    소녀 "\"...Are you okay?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:526
translate english chapter7_a49aa00e:

    # voice ""
    # "이번엔 소녀의 목소리가, 환청처럼 귓가를 맴돈다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl's voice echoed in my ears, like a hallucination."

# game/chapter7.rpy:528
translate english chapter7_af26a899:

    # "왠지 눈을 뜨면 더는 그 목소리가 들려오지 않을 것 같아, 그 자리에서 생각을 멈추고, 귀를 기울였다. "
    "For some reason, I felt that if I opened my eyes, I would no longer hear that voice. So I stayed put, stopped thinking, and listened carefully."

# game/chapter7.rpy:532
translate english chapter7_a21984bc:

    # voice "voices/gg35.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“대답 좀 해달라니까요?!”"
    voice "voices/gg35.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I asked you to respond!\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:534
translate english chapter7_9780732e:

    # voice ""
    # "그 목소리와 함께 양팔에 느껴진 익숙한 감촉이 나의 정신을 깨웠다. "
    voice ""
    "Along with her voice, the familiar sensation on my arms woke me up."

# game/chapter7.rpy:541
translate english chapter7_4e98ef64:

    # 나 "“…… 아, 으응.”"
    나 "\"...Ah, uh...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:543
translate english chapter7_3de5d785:

    # voice "voices/gg36.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아까부터 아무런 말도 안 해서…… 걱정했잖아요?!”"
    voice "voices/gg36.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You haven't said anything since earlier... I was worried!\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:549
translate english chapter7_f30dabbd:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀답지 않은, 격앙된 목소리였다. "
    voice ""
    "Her voice was filled with an uncharacteristic intensity."

# game/chapter7.rpy:551
translate english chapter7_448d7e3b:

    # "손을 뻗어, 소녀의 어깨 위로 올린다. "
    "I reached out and placed my hand on the girl's shoulder."

# game/chapter7.rpy:556
translate english chapter7_d13825ae:

    # "{color=#00ccff}소녀는 분명 이곳에 존재했다.{/color} "
    "{color=#00ccff}The girl was undoubtedly here.{/color}"

# game/chapter7.rpy:561
translate english chapter7_17ca21e7:

    # 나 "“어떻게 된 거야?”"
    나 "\"What happened?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:562
translate english chapter7_28a4101e:

    # voice "voices/gg37.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그건 오히려 제가 묻고 싶은 거라고요. 아무리 불러도 대답 안 하길래, 뭐가 잘못되기라도 한 줄 알고…….”"
    voice "voices/gg37.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I should be the one asking that. I kept calling you but you didn't respond. I thought something went wrong...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:564
translate english chapter7_204f3a0e:

    # voice ""
    # "금방이라도 울음을 터뜨릴 것 같은 소녀의 눈동자는 티 없이 순수한 진실만을 말하고 있었다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl's eyes, as if they were about to burst into tears, spoke only of pure, unadulterated truth."

# game/chapter7.rpy:570
translate english chapter7_9fbbee4d:

    # "살며시 뻗어진 손가락이 소녀의 뺨을 매만진다. "
    "Gently extended fingers traced the girl's cheek."

# game/chapter7.rpy:571
translate english chapter7_14e36c1d:

    # "보드라운 감촉이, 그녀의 존재를 내 손가락에 다시금 각인시켰다. "
    "The soft touch once again etched her existence into my fingertips."

# game/chapter7.rpy:572
translate english chapter7_df712e74:

    # "우습게도, 기뻤다. "
    "Ridiculously enough, I was happy."

# game/chapter7.rpy:573
translate english chapter7_fffafd51:

    # "소녀가 아직 사라지지 않고, 나의 앞에 존재한다는 사실이. "
    "That the girl had not yet disappeared and was still in front of me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:574
translate english chapter7_263195cd:

    # "우스울 정도로, 그리고 한편으로는 한심할 정도로 기뻤다. "
    "I was happy to the point of being silly and at the same time pathetic."

# game/chapter7.rpy:575
translate english chapter7_9110d4a2:

    # "소녀에게서 손을 떼어낸 나는, 멋쩍은 웃음을 지어 보였다. "
    "Pulling my hand away from the girl, I forced a sheepish smile."

# game/chapter7.rpy:577
translate english chapter7_9d0aac6b:

    # 나 "“…… 잠깐 다른 생각 하고 있었어.”"
    나 "\"... I was just lost in thought for a moment.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:579
translate english chapter7_56c0134e:

    # voice "voices/gg38.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“정말이죠?”"
    voice "voices/gg38.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Really?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:581
translate english chapter7_c18ef082:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응. 앞으론 조심할게.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Uh-huh. I'll be careful from now on.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:584
translate english chapter7_ed99c984:

    # "나의 얼굴을 유심히 살피던 소녀도, 한층 가벼워진 내 표정을 읽고선 걱정하던 기색을 거두었다. "
    "The girl who had been scrutinizing my face also relaxed her worried look after reading my considerably lightened expression."

# game/chapter7.rpy:586
translate english chapter7_60b3596d:

    # voice "voices/gg39.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그 목소리는 들려왔나요?”"
    voice "voices/gg39.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Did you hear that voice?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:588
translate english chapter7_6da2f2ff:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아니……. 넌 뭔가 기억난 거라도 있어?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"No... Do you remember something?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:591
translate english chapter7_f3d6929f:

    # voice "voices/gg40.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아뇨. 아무것도요.”"
    voice "voices/gg40.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No. Nothing at all.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:593
translate english chapter7_94e53581:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그런가. 아무래도 이번 방법은 실패한 것 같네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I see. It seems like this method was a failure.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:596
translate english chapter7_0e49e97f:

    # "혹시나 하는 생각에 주변을 둘러보았지만, 나를 반기는 건 전혀 달라지지 않은 폐전신국과 주변의 풍경이었다. "
    "Hoping against hope, I looked around, but all that greeted me was the unchanging abandoned telegraph station and the surrounding scenery."

# game/chapter7.rpy:598
translate english chapter7_32c292d1:

    # voice "voices/gg41.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이제 다음 계획은 뭔가요?”"
    voice "voices/gg41.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What's the next plan?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:600
translate english chapter7_959327df:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 글쎄.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...I don't know.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:610
translate english chapter7_dfe5a396:

    # "소녀와 함께 아까 앉았던 벤치로 향한 나는, ‘그 목소리’에 대한 생각을 이어갔다. "
    "As I headed towards the bench where I had sat with the girl earlier, I continued to ponder over 'that voice'."

# game/chapter7.rpy:611
translate english chapter7_5d76e29e:

    # "정확히는, 이어가려 했다는 편이 맞을 것이다. "
    "To be precise, it would be more accurate to say that I was trying to continue."

# game/chapter7.rpy:612
translate english chapter7_1a4bc468:

    # "생각은 전혀 쌓이지 못한 채 시간만이 착실히 흘러가고 있었다. "
    "Thoughts were not accumulating at all; only time was steadily passing by."

# game/chapter7.rpy:613
translate english chapter7_badcc122:

    # "조금이나마 생각이 쌓이려는 기미가 보이면, 그 생각의 조각들은 금세 바람에 불려 날아갈 뿐이었다. "
    "Whenever there seemed to be a hint of thoughts gathering, those fragments of thought were quickly blown away by the wind."

# game/chapter7.rpy:617
translate english chapter7_49191de9:

    # "소녀가 잠깐이나마 사라졌다고 착각했던 그 순간의 일이, 머릿속에서 날카로운 바람이 되어 생각의 조각을 산산이 흩날렸다. "
    "The moment when I mistakenly thought that the girl had disappeared for a while turned into a sharp wind in my head, scattering my thoughts into pieces."

# game/chapter7.rpy:618
translate english chapter7_62cdfd47:

    # "이래서야, 아무리 생각해도 떠오르는 건 없을 것 같았다. "
    "At this rate, it seemed unlikely that anything would come to mind no matter how much I thought about it."

# game/chapter7.rpy:619
translate english chapter7_796d2d63:

    # "소득 없이, 제법 긴 시간이 흘렀다. "
    "Without any progress, a considerable amount of time had passed."

# game/chapter7.rpy:630
translate english chapter7_faece166:

    # 나 "“…… 잘 모르겠어.”"
    나 "\"... I'm not sure.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:632
translate english chapter7_510b4fa0:

    # voice "voices/gg42.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런가요.”"
    voice "voices/gg42.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I see.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:635
translate english chapter7_411d5753:

    # voice ""
    # "마냥 편안한 얼굴로 불어오는 바람에 머리카락을 나부끼고 있던 소녀가, 무릎을 앞뒤로 까닥이며 대답했다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl, who had been swaying her hair in the wind with a relaxed expression on her face, replied as she swung her knees back and forth."

# game/chapter7.rpy:640
translate english chapter7_69304ec3:

    # voice "voices/gg43.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“결국, 원하던 건 못 이루고 돌아가게 됐네요.”"
    voice "voices/gg43.ogg"
    소녀 "\"In the end, we couldn't achieve what we wanted and had to go back.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:642
translate english chapter7_085c8575:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그러게.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Seems so.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:645
translate english chapter7_8496a388:

    # voice "voices/gg44.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럼, 조금만 더 있다 가요.”"
    voice "voices/gg44.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Then, let's stay a little longer before we leave.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:647
translate english chapter7_93c52927:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 그럴까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... Maybe we should.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:650
translate english chapter7_f9c58fbd:

    # "익숙한 부탁이었다. "
    "It was a familiar request."

# game/chapter7.rpy:651
translate english chapter7_ad7416a1:

    # "거절할 이유가 없었기에, 나는 일말의 생각조차 놓아버리고는 그저 다른 곳을 바라보고 있던 소녀를 멍하니 쳐다보았다. "
    "Having no reason to refuse, I absentmindedly stared at the girl who was looking elsewhere without giving it a second thought."

# game/chapter7.rpy:653
translate english chapter7_c1355fa6:

    # voice "voices/gg45.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“좋네요. 이런 거.”"
    voice "voices/gg45.ogg"
    소녀 "\"This is nice. Things like this.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:659
translate english chapter7_86a04c05:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀의 말을 곧이곧대로 받아들이지 못한 나는, 힐긋 고개를 돌려 그녀가 바라보고 있던 곳으로 시선을 향한다. "
    voice ""
    "Unable to take the girl's words at face value, I turned my head slightly and directed my gaze towards where she was looking."

# game/chapter7.rpy:661
translate english chapter7_bd57322e:

    # "그와 동시에 고개를 옆으로 향한 소녀가, 그대로 나와 시선을 마주친다. "
    "At the same time, the girl, who had turned her head to the side, locked eyes with me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:663
translate english chapter7_4f95ab1b:

    # "어색하게 시선을 돌렸다. "
    "I awkwardly averted my gaze."

# game/chapter7.rpy:664
translate english chapter7_98fa77ab:

    # "그러고는 벤치에 손가락을 툭툭 맞대며, 소녀가 내뱉은 말의 의미를 고민했다. "
    "Then, tapping my fingers on the bench, I pondered the meaning of the words the girl had uttered."

# game/chapter7.rpy:665
translate english chapter7_e72cf222:

    # "‘이런’ 건, 무엇을 의미하는 것일까? "
    "What could 'this' mean?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:666
translate english chapter7_cd4cc146:

    # "좋다는 건, 어떤 감정을 의미하는 것일까? "
    "What emotion does 'good' imply?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:668
translate english chapter7_a6b8853e:

    # voice "voices/gg46.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“뭘 그렇게 고민하고 있는 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/gg46.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What are you pondering so much about?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:670
translate english chapter7_8d527964:

    # voice ""
    # "바람에 뒤섞여, 소녀의 목소리가 들려온다. "
    voice ""
    "Her voice reached me, mingled with the wind."

# game/chapter7.rpy:676
translate english chapter7_2cd96262:

    # 나 "“네가 말한 ‘이런’ 게 뭔지 고민하고 있었어.”"
    나 "\"I was wondering what you meant by 'this'.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:678
translate english chapter7_afa4446a:

    # voice "voices/gg47.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“말했잖아요. 이렇게 있으면, 편안해진다고요.”"
    voice "voices/gg47.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I told you. When it's like this, it feels comfortable.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:680
translate english chapter7_4820c7b1:

    # voice ""
    # "한쪽 어깨에, 소녀의 체중이 실린다. "
    voice ""
    "I felt the weight of the girl on one shoulder."

# game/chapter7.rpy:683
translate english chapter7_9ff56ef5:

    # "이 순간만큼은 자신이 영원을 떠돌던 유령이라는 사실을 잊기라도 한 건지."
    "For this moment at least, it was as if she had forgotten that she was a ghost wandering eternity."

# game/chapter7.rpy:684
translate english chapter7_1c1ba541:

    # "정말, 소녀는 편안해 보였다. "
    "Indeed, the girl looked comfortable."

# game/chapter7.rpy:686
translate english chapter7_72c6e016:

    # 나 "“걱정되진 않고?”"
    나 "\"Aren't you worried?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:687
translate english chapter7_d7402f54:

    # voice "voices/gg48.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“걱정돼요.”"
    voice "voices/gg48.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I am worried.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:689
translate english chapter7_ab598fc0:

    # voice ""
    # "어깨에 기대어 눈을 지그시 감은 채, 소녀는 나지막이 대답했다. "
    voice ""
    "Leaning on my shoulder with her eyes slightly closed, the girl replied softly."

# game/chapter7.rpy:692
translate english chapter7_c4b824ba:

    # 나 "“…… 미안.”"
    나 "\"... I'm sorry.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:694
translate english chapter7_128e642e:

    # "그런 무책임한 말을 나도 모르게 내뱉었다는 사실에 놀랐다. "
    "I was surprised that I had unwittingly blurted out such irresponsible words."

# game/chapter7.rpy:696
translate english chapter7_77c2d0bc:

    # "소녀는 만약 내가 그녀가 사라지지 않았다는 걸 깨달았을 때 안도감을 느꼈다는 사실을 알게 된다면, 뭐라고 반응할까? "
    "If the girl knew that I felt relieved when I realized she hadn't disappeared, how would she react?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:697
translate english chapter7_b3b2ec23:

    # "미묘한 감각의 소용돌이가 휘몰아쳐 왔다. "
    "A whirlwind of subtle sensations swept over me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:698
translate english chapter7_a6c3c87f:

    # "하지만 미묘한 감각의 소용돌이 속에서 소녀로부터 들려온 대답은, 예상과는 많이 동떨어져 있었다. "
    "However, the response from the girl within this whirlwind of subtle sensations was far from what I had expected."

# game/chapter7.rpy:704
translate english chapter7_7a7c68c1:

    # voice "voices/gg49.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“미안하면, 앞으로 그러지 마세요.”"
    voice "voices/gg49.ogg"
    소녀 "\"If you're sorry, then don't do it again.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:706
translate english chapter7_939e1ce7:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 무슨 뜻이야?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... What do you mean?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:709
translate english chapter7_734d2cba:

    # "나는 이번에도 소녀의 말을 이해하지 못했다. "
    "Once again, I failed to understand the girl's words."

# game/chapter7.rpy:710
translate english chapter7_4d39e94a:

    # "내가 모르는 사이에, ‘네가 사라지지 않아 다행이야.’ 같은 이야기를 건네기라도 했던 것일까? "
    "Had I unknowingly conveyed something like 'I'm glad you haven't disappeared' to her?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:712
translate english chapter7_d964d747:

    # voice "voices/gg50.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 제가 걱정할만한 일, 하지 말라고요. 막무가내로 높은 곳에서 떨어져 보려고 하지도 말고, 멍하니 있으면서 제 말 무시도 하지 말아 줬으면 좋겠어요.”"
    voice "voices/gg50.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... I wish you wouldn't do things that make me worry. Don't try to fall from high places recklessly, and I'd appreciate it if you didn't ignore what I say while spacing out.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:714
translate english chapter7_0b16843e:

    # voice ""
    # "익숙한 느낌이 드는 이야기였다. "
    voice ""
    "It was a familiar sentiment."

# game/chapter7.rpy:716
translate english chapter7_4dc62023:

    # "자신을 위해 무리하지 말라는 식의 이야기를, 나는 이미 귀에 딱지가 앉도록 들어왔지만. "
    "I've heard such pleas not to overdo it for my own sake until I was sick of them."

# game/chapter7.rpy:717
translate english chapter7_481123cd:

    # "바로 지금, 나의 어깨에 기댄 소녀가 나지막이 전해주는 이 이야기는, 여태껏 들어왔던 그것과는 조금 다른 느낌이었다. "
    "However, the story that the girl, leaning on my shoulder right now, quietly relayed felt slightly different from what I had heard so far."

# game/chapter7.rpy:719
translate english chapter7_2eccf591:

    # voice "voices/gg51.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“정말 그 높은 곳에서 직접 떨어지려고 생각했던 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gg51.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Did you really consider falling from such a high place yourself?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:721
translate english chapter7_1ec245ce:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“응. 그거 말곤 딱히 떠오르는 게 없었으니까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah. There wasn't anything else that came to mind.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:724
translate english chapter7_4f79c2c7:

    # voice "voices/gg52.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“너무 위험하잖아요, 그런 거.”"
    voice "voices/gg52.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's too dangerous.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:726
translate english chapter7_b1eafd86:

    # 나 "“지금 생각해보니 그런 것 같기도 하고.”"
    나 "\"Thinking about it now, it does seem that way.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:727
translate english chapter7_ec527656:

    # voice ""
    # "무책임한 한마디에 책임을 묻기라도 하듯, 어깨에 툭 하고는 가벼운 손길이 느껴졌다. "
    voice ""
    "As if to hold me accountable for my irresponsible remark, I felt a light touch on my shoulder."

# game/chapter7.rpy:730
translate english chapter7_13b0174c:

    # voice "voices/gg53.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“지금에 와서 너무 늦은 것 같긴 하지만.”"
    voice "voices/gg53.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It seems too late now though.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:732
translate english chapter7_0ff6d485:

    # voice ""
    # "스르르 흘러내린 소녀의 손길이 나의 손등에 닿았다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl's hand slid down and touched the back of my hand."

# game/chapter7.rpy:735
translate english chapter7_3c3c269e:

    # voice "voices/gg54.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“소원을 바꾸고 싶어요.”"
    voice "voices/gg54.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I want to change my wish.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:737
translate english chapter7_3c2a02fb:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 손등을 덮은 소녀의 손은 마치 한겨울을 이불처럼 감싼 눈송이처럼 차갑고도, 따뜻했다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl's hand, which covered the back of my hand, was as cold and warm as a snowflake enveloping a winter quilt."

# game/chapter7.rpy:740
translate english chapter7_2e0a9804:

    # 나 "“…… 어째서?”"
    나 "\"... Why?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:742
translate english chapter7_dc0460c7:

    # voice "voices/gg55.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“소원이 뭔지 들어볼 생각은 없는 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gg55.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Don't you want to hear what my wish is?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:744
translate english chapter7_1f2520ec:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“알겠어. 소원이 뭔데.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Alright. What's your wish.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:747
translate english chapter7_aadabfa6:

    # "나의 손 위에 겹쳐져 온기를 찾는 소녀의 손이 희미하게 꼼지락대는 것이 느껴졌다. "
    "I could feel the girl's hand, which was overlaid on mine, faintly fidgeting in search of warmth."

# game/chapter7.rpy:749
translate english chapter7_30a3cffe:

    # voice "voices/gg56.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이런 일은, 이제 그만했으면 좋겠어요.”"
    voice "voices/gg56.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I wish you would stop doing this.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:751
translate english chapter7_b31b79c5:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“이런 일이라니?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Doing what?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:754
translate english chapter7_6d15705c:

    # voice "voices/gg57.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“제 기억을 찾아주기 위해, 그리고 저를 없애주기 위해 더 애써주지 않아도 괜찮아요. 아니, 그러지 말아 주세요. 어제도 말했다고요. 과잉친절이라고…….”"
    voice "voices/gg57.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You don't have to try so hard to find my memories and make me disappear. No, please don't. I told you yesterday as well. It's excessive kindness...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:756
translate english chapter7_0b14326d:

    # voice ""
    # "시선을 내리고, 맞잡은 두 손에 시선을 고정하고선 소녀가 말했다. "
    voice ""
    "Lowering her gaze and focusing on our intertwined hands, the girl spoke."

# game/chapter7.rpy:759
translate english chapter7_7da59b3e:

    # voice "voices/gg58.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이젠 뭘 해야 할지도 모르잖아요. 언젠가 돌아가야 한다고도 했고. 그럼 그때까지…… 정말 해야만 하는 일들을 해주세요.”"
    voice "voices/gg58.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Now I don't even know what I should do. I told you that at some point I have to go back. So until then... please do only what you really have to do.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:762
translate english chapter7_b45a3987:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 이야기와 함께 고개를 든 소녀가 싱긋 웃어 보였다. "
    voice ""
    "With those words, the girl who lifted her head gave a faint smile."

# game/chapter7.rpy:765
translate english chapter7_e53af9bf:

    # voice "voices/gg59.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“전 저를 위해 이렇게나 애써줬던 사람이 있다는 것만으로 충분히 행복해요.”"
    voice "voices/gg59.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I'm already happy enough just knowing that there was someone who cared for me this much.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:767
translate english chapter7_0f301448:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀의 웃음에 뭐라 반응해야 할지 몰라 고개를 돌리려는데. "
    voice ""
    "Not knowing how to respond to the girl's laughter, I tried to turn my head away. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:770
translate english chapter7_5c6695a4:

    # "무방비해진 나의 뺨에 소녀의 얼굴이 기습적으로 가까워졌다. "
    "Unexpectedly, the girl's face came close to my unprotected cheek. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:772
translate english chapter7_89d0bb79:

    # "그러고는 그녀의 입술이, 잠깐, 아주 잠깐 나의 뺨에 닿는다. "
    "Then her lips touched my cheek for a moment, just a brief moment. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:779
translate english chapter7_618393e7:

    # voice "voices/gg60.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이건, 어제의 좋아한다는 말에 대한 대답이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gg60.ogg"
    소녀 "\"This is... a response to your confession of love yesterday.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:781
translate english chapter7_1fbf0303:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:783
translate english chapter7_5f94cbf7:

    # voice "voices/gg61.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그러니까, 부탁해요.”"
    voice "voices/gg61.ogg"
    소녀 "\"So, please.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:785
translate english chapter7_d59f986c:

    # voice ""
    # "멋대로였던 방금의 행동이 부끄러웠는지, 소녀는 고개를 숙인 채 작은 목소리로 말했다. "
    voice ""
    "Perhaps embarrassed by her sudden action just now, the girl spoke in a small voice with her head bowed. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:788
translate english chapter7_3e80e2f3:

    # "나는 고개를 끄덕인다거나, 알겠다고 말하는 대신 소녀가 내게 했던 것과 똑같은 방식의 대답을 그녀에게 건넸다. "
    "Instead of nodding or saying okay, I gave her the same kind of response she had given me. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:790
translate english chapter7_c051097d:

    # "좋은 향이 났다. "
    "It smelled good. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:795
translate english chapter7_7d5a0175:

    # "쌉싸름한 바람의 향기에 덧대진 소녀의 달콤한 향기는, 정말이지 기분 좋은 향이었다. "
    "The sweet scent of the girl overlaid on the bitter wind was truly a pleasant fragrance. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:810
translate english chapter7_4a93b434:

    # "철조망을 넘어, 골목길을 내려오고, 아치교를 건너며 주변을 둘러볼 때까지만 해도 세상은 아무런 변함 없이, 인공 개울이 흘러가듯 자연스레 흘러가는 것만 같았다. "
    "Even as I crossed over the iron fence, descended the alleyway, and looked around while crossing the arch bridge, the world seemed to flow naturally like an artificial stream without any change. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:811
translate english chapter7_ee60156c:

    # "막상 위화감을 느끼기 시작한 건, F구역의 터미널에 도착하고 난 직후였다. "
    "The moment I started feeling out of place was right after arriving at terminal F district. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:818
translate english chapter7_a52f0b91:

    # 나 "“…… 좀 이상하지 않아?”"
    나 "\"... Doesn't it seem a bit strange?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:820
translate english chapter7_2dd4aaeb:

    # voice "voices/gg62.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이상하다니요?”"
    voice "voices/gg62.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Strange, you say?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:822
translate english chapter7_276e59ce:

    # voice ""
    # "내 말의 의도조차 알지 못하겠다는 듯 고개를 갸웃대는 소녀. "
    voice ""
    "The girl tilts her head as if she doesn't even understand the intent of my words."

# game/chapter7.rpy:824
translate english chapter7_05747541:

    # "아리송한 표정으로 주변을 살피는 소녀에게서는 일말의 이상함도 느껴지지 않았다. "
    "There was no trace of strangeness felt from the girl who was looking around with a perplexed expression."

# game/chapter7.rpy:826
translate english chapter7_2527ec84:

    # 나 "“그런가.”"
    나 "'Is that so?'"

# game/chapter7.rpy:836
translate english chapter7_c2fa89d4:

    # "마치 무인 세계의 연장선이기라도 한 듯 조용한 역내를, 나는 어색하게 걸었다. "
    "As if it were an extension of a deserted world, I walked awkwardly through the quiet station."

# game/chapter7.rpy:837
translate english chapter7_07ee3979:

    # "단순한 비유가 아니었다. "
    "It was not a simple metaphor."

# game/chapter7.rpy:838
translate english chapter7_2710d31b:

    # "단 한 사람의 그림자조차 보이지 않는 역사는, 말 그대로 텅 비어 있었다. "
    "The station, where not even a single shadow could be seen, was literally empty."

# game/chapter7.rpy:839
translate english chapter7_edb471be:

    # "아무리 F구역의 터미널에 인적이 드물다고는 해도, 이렇게까지 인기척조차 느껴보지 못했던 적은 열차가 모두 끊기고 난 뒤가 아니면 없었는데 말이다. "
    "Even though the terminal of F district is rarely crowded, there had never been a time when I could not feel any human presence to this extent unless all the trains had stopped."

# game/chapter7.rpy:840
translate english chapter7_ea615f2a:

    # "하지만 아무도 보는 이가 없음에도 개의치 않고 움직이는 시계처럼, 역내는 바삐 돌아가고 있었다. "
    "However, like a clock that moves without anyone watching it, the station was bustling."

# game/chapter7.rpy:846
translate english chapter7_815413ea:

    # "역내의 안내방송이 들려오고, 반대편의 열차가 정차하고, 목적지로 향하는 방향의 열차가 도착한다. "
    "The station's announcements could be heard, trains stopped on the opposite side, and trains arrived in the direction of their destination."

# game/chapter7.rpy:850
translate english chapter7_88d5ee47:

    # "열차는 아무런 일도 없었다는 듯 담담히 선로를 달렸다. "
    "The train ran along the tracks as if nothing had happened."

# game/chapter7.rpy:851
translate english chapter7_7b2b4b1c:

    # "햇살을 받으며, 잠깐 잠에 들었다. "
    "Basking in the sunlight, I fell into a brief sleep."

# game/chapter7.rpy:852
translate english chapter7_1be55666:

    # "종착지인 A구역 터미널에 도착했을 땐, 나의 앞에 서 있던 소녀가 내 어깨를 두드리며 잠을 깨우고 있었다. "
    "When we arrived at the terminal in A district, our final destination, the girl standing before me was rousing me from sleep by tapping my shoulder."

# game/chapter7.rpy:858
translate english chapter7_efeb55d1:

    # "꿈이라도 꿨냐는 듯, 주변에는 바쁘게 움직이는 사람들이 잔뜩이었다. "
    "As if I had been dreaming, there were plenty of people bustling around me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:861
translate english chapter7_dd3faf30:

    # 나 "“아얏…….”"
    나 "\"Ouch...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:863
translate english chapter7_aefb47d9:

    # "자리에서 일어나 열차 밖으로 나가려는데, 흐릿한 감각이 뒷덜미를 스쳤다. "
    "As I got up from my seat and tried to leave the train, a hazy sensation brushed against the back of my head."

# game/chapter7.rpy:870
translate english chapter7_9c310169:

    # voice "voices/gg63.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“왜 그래요?”"
    voice "voices/gg63.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What's wrong?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:872
translate english chapter7_5c405a57:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 그때 조금 근육이 놀랐나 봐.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... Seems like my muscles were startled back then.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:875
translate english chapter7_b2aedc54:

    # voice "voices/gg64.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“거봐요, 위험했잖아요.”"
    voice "voices/gg64.ogg"
    소녀 "\"See? That was risky.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:877
translate english chapter7_120b6345:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응…… 그렇네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Um... Yeah.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:884
translate english chapter7_25220182:

    # "그렇게 대답하긴 했지만, 자신 없는 목소리였다. "
    "Although I responded as such, my voice lacked conviction."

# game/chapter7.rpy:885
translate english chapter7_e447fad3:

    # "분명 방금 잠에서 깨어났는데, 꿈을 꾸듯 모호한 느낌이었다. "
    "Even though I had just woken up from sleep, it felt vague as if I had been dreaming."

# game/chapter7.rpy:889
translate english chapter7_7a83c912:

    # "바람이라도 불면 사라질 것처럼, 인기척으로부터 느껴지는 모든 감각이 흐릿했다. "
    "As if it would disappear with a gust of wind, all sensations felt from human presence were blurred."

# game/chapter7.rpy:890
translate english chapter7_2c7ac5d2:

    # "머리를 거칠게 양옆으로 흔들고선, 역 바깥을 향했다. "
    "I shook my head roughly side to side, then turned towards the outside of the station."

# game/chapter7.rpy:891
translate english chapter7_5a10f3fc:

    # "나의 손을 잡은 소녀가, 사뿐사뿐 발걸음을 옮겼다. "
    "The girl who held my hand moved her steps lightly."

# game/chapter7.rpy:900
translate english chapter7_b33ea3b7:

    # "역 근처 횡단보도를 건너 큰길을 걸을 때까지도, 꿈속을 걷는 듯한 느낌은 지워질 기색을 보이지 않았다. "
    "Even while crossing the crosswalk near the station and walking on the main road, the feeling as if I was walking in a dream didn't seem to fade away."

# game/chapter7.rpy:901
translate english chapter7_8740c117:

    # "모든 것이 아득한 느낌이었다. "
    "Everything felt distant."

# game/chapter7.rpy:902
translate english chapter7_741eeb43:

    # "멀리서 들려오는 발걸음 소리도, 눈앞을 스쳐 지나가는 이름 모를 사람의 인기척도, 등 뒤에서 들려오는, 나를 부르는 목소리도……. "
    "The sound of footsteps coming from afar, the presence of nameless people passing by in front of me, and even the voice calling me from behind..."

# game/chapter7.rpy:908
translate english chapter7_84b7f327:

    # "그 목소리에 먼저 반응을 보인 건 소녀 쪽이었다. "
    "The girl was the first to react to that voice."

# game/chapter7.rpy:910
translate english chapter7_79d23801:

    # "소녀가 고개를 뒤를 돌아본 이후에서야, 나는 한발 늦게 고개를 돌려 그곳을 바라보았다. "
    "Only after the girl turned her head back did I belatedly turn mine to look in that direction."

# game/chapter7.rpy:913
translate english chapter7_cdfd0240:

    # "조금 떨어진 거리에서, 유미가 손을 흔들며 걸어오는 것이 보였다. "
    "At a slight distance, I could see Yumi walking towards us while waving her hand."

# game/chapter7.rpy:922
translate english chapter7_87dde787:

    # voice "voices/yg1.ogg"
    # 유미 "“오늘은 이런 곳에서 보네?”"
    voice "voices/yg1.ogg"
    유미 "\"So we meet here today?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:924
translate english chapter7_0a6e865f:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 앞에 선 유미는 저편에서부터 빠른 걸음으로 나를 쫓아왔던 건지 약간은 가쁜 호흡으로 인사를 꺼냈다. "
    voice ""
    "Yumi who stood before me greeted with slightly heavy breathing. It seemed she had been chasing after me from afar with quick steps."

# game/chapter7.rpy:926
translate english chapter7_c30c0be6:

    # "어디서부터 유미는 나를 발견했던 걸까. "
    "I wonder where Yumi had spotted me from."

# game/chapter7.rpy:927
translate english chapter7_cc5c66e1:

    # "슬그머니 주홍빛을 머금어가던 주변을 휙 둘러본 나는, 숨을 고르고 있던 유미에게 말을 건넸다. "
    "As I casually looked around at the surroundings starting to take on a rosy hue, I spoke to Yumi who was catching her breath."

# game/chapter7.rpy:929
translate english chapter7_12c5e040:

    # 나 "“그러게. 늘 보던 곳에서만 봤었지……. 그나저나 바쁠 텐데, 여기까진 웬일로 나온 거야?”"
    나 "\"Right. We've only ever met in our usual spot... By the way, you must be busy. What brings you out here?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:931
translate english chapter7_78fa4c7d:

    # voice "voices/yg2.ogg"
    # 유미 "“아아, 그게~ 저기 공원에서 잠깐 산책이나 한다고.”"
    voice "voices/yg2.ogg"
    유미 "\"Ah, well~ I was just taking a little walk in the park.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:933
translate english chapter7_a7eaac9f:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“다이어트라도 하려고?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Trying to lose weight or something?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:936
translate english chapter7_c602463f:

    # voice "voices/yg3.ogg"
    # 유미 "“그런 건 아니고. 말 그대로 잠깐 산책만 하러 나온 거야.”"
    voice "voices/yg3.ogg"
    유미 "\"No, not really. I just came out for a walk, that's all.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:938
translate english chapter7_657a98f3:

    # voice ""
    # "심호흡으로 숨 고르기를 마무리한 유미가 발걸음을 옮기기 시작했고, 나도, 소녀도, 멈췄던 움직임을 계속했다. "
    voice ""
    "Having caught her breath with deep inhales and exhales, Yumi started moving again, and so did I and the girl, resuming our halted steps."

# game/chapter7.rpy:946
translate english chapter7_5c6f05b0:

    # 나 "“아무런 이유도 없이 산책이라니, 조금 안 어울리네.”"
    나 "\"Taking a walk for no particular reason doesn't seem like you.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:948
translate english chapter7_7fbe1f20:

    # voice "voices/yg4.ogg"
    # 유미 "“안 어울린다니, 어떤 면에서?”"
    voice "voices/yg4.ogg"
    유미 "\"Doesn't suit me? In what way?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:950
translate english chapter7_dbc43482:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아, 으음……. 글쎄.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ah, um... Well...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:953
translate english chapter7_25a8f3f8:

    # "유미는 가벼운 웃음을 지어 보이더니, 곧바로 대화의 방향을 틀었다. "
    "Yumi displayed a light smile before quickly changing the direction of the conversation."

# game/chapter7.rpy:956
translate english chapter7_81be43fd:

    # voice "voices/yg5.ogg"
    # 유미 "“너는 어디 가는 길이었어?”"
    voice "voices/yg5.ogg"
    유미 "\"So where were you headed?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:961
translate english chapter7_411a7692:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그냥, 집 가는 중이었지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Just on my way home.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:964
translate english chapter7_65dbf414:

    # voice "voices/yg6.ogg"
    # 유미 "“그럼, 질문을 바꿔서. 어디 갔다 오는 길이었어?”"
    voice "voices/yg6.ogg"
    유미 "\"Then let me rephrase. Where were you coming from?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:966
translate english chapter7_85ea1cf4:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“전에 들렀던 폐전신국에 갔다 오는 중이었어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I was just coming back from the abandoned telegraph station.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:969
translate english chapter7_487a07d3:

    # voice "voices/yg7.ogg"
    # 유미 "“폐전신국? 근처에 그런 곳이 있었어?”"
    voice "voices/yg7.ogg"
    유미 "\"Abandoned telegraph station? Was there such a place around here?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:971
translate english chapter7_19851466:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어…… 그때 그 장소 말이야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Uh... I'm talking about that place from before.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:979
translate english chapter7_88020a5a:

    # "잠깐 생각에 잠겼던 유미가 정답을 찾기까지는 그리 오랜 시간이 걸리지 않았다. "
    "Yumi, who had been momentarily lost in thought, didn't take long to find the answer."

# game/chapter7.rpy:986
translate english chapter7_7533c405:

    # voice "voices/yg8.ogg"
    # 유미 "“아, 그때 그 장소가 폐전신국 앞이었구나. 그때는 정신이 없어서 거기가 전신국이었던 줄도 몰랐어.”"
    voice "voices/yg8.ogg"
    유미 "\"Ah, so that place was in front of the abandoned telegraph station. I was so out of it back then that I didn't even realize it was a telegraph station.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:988
translate english chapter7_3bc1f672:

    # voice ""
    # "머쓱한 표정을 지은 유미가 내 맞은편을 힐긋 바라보았다. "
    voice ""
    "With a sheepish expression, Yumi glanced at me from across."

# game/chapter7.rpy:995
translate english chapter7_fd91bc89:

    # voice "voices/yg9.ogg"
    # 유미 "“그럼, 지금 네 옆에 그 유령도 같이 있겠네?”"
    voice "voices/yg9.ogg"
    유미 "\"So, is that ghost with you now?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:997
translate english chapter7_f897d660:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응, 그렇지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Uh-huh, yes.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1000
translate english chapter7_13b0dde7:

    # voice "voices/yg10.ogg"
    # 유미 "“어떻게 됐어?”"
    voice "voices/yg10.ogg"
    유미 "\"What happened?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1002
translate english chapter7_080e540c:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“잘 안 됐어. 그냥 빈손으로 돌아오는 길이었거든.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It didn't go well. I'm just on my way back empty-handed.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1005
translate english chapter7_3b8589e1:

    # voice "voices/yg11.ogg"
    # 유미 "“흐음…… 그렇구나…….”"
    voice "voices/yg11.ogg"
    유미 "\"Hmm... I see...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1011
translate english chapter7_1b1bbb47:

    # voice ""
    # "그럭저럭 흘러가던 대화가 미묘한 분위기에 부딪혀 그 자리에 멈춰 선다. "
    voice ""
    "The conversation that had been flowing somewhat smoothly hits a peculiar atmosphere and comes to a standstill."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1014
translate english chapter7_4a689f91:

    # "평소의 유미 같았다면 무작정 내게 힘내라는 말이라도 해줄 줄 알았는데. "
    "I thought Yumi, as usual, would have told me to cheer up without hesitation. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:1016
translate english chapter7_1319a84f:

    # "내 쪽을 머뭇머뭇 살피던 유미가, 자그마한 목소리로 말을 꺼냈다. "
    "Yumi, who had been hesitantly observing me, spoke up in a tiny voice. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:1022
translate english chapter7_f7edef13:

    # voice "voices/yg12.ogg"
    # 유미 "“나도 그런데. 비슷한 처지네.”"
    voice "voices/yg12.ogg"
    유미 "\"I'm in a similar situation too.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1024
translate english chapter7_29f07077:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Huh?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1031
translate english chapter7_99c6ac48:

    # voice "voices/yg13.ogg"
    # 유미 "“아, 아냐. 그냥 투정 부려 본 거야. 신경 안 써도 돼.”"
    voice "voices/yg13.ogg"
    유미 "\"Ah, no, never mind. I was just being petulant. Don't worry about it.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1033
translate english chapter7_e6883a9e:

    # voice ""
    # "내가 뭐라 말을 덧붙이기도 전에, 유미는 대화를 끊어버리고는 손사래와 인사 사이의 어중간한 손짓을 흔들어 보였다. "
    voice ""
    "Before I could add anything else, Yumi cut off the conversation and waved her hand somewhere between a wave and a greeting. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:1036
translate english chapter7_f2f25c86:

    # voice "voices/yg14.ogg"
    # 유미 "“그럼 난 먼저 가볼게. 다음에 봐~”"
    voice "voices/yg14.ogg"
    유미 "\"Well then, I'll be going first. See you later~\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1041
translate english chapter7_71bc8a97:

    # voice ""
    # "깜빡이는 신호등 사이의 인파 속으로 뛰어가 사라져가는 유미. "
    voice ""
    "Yumi disappeared into the crowd between the blinking traffic lights. "

# game/chapter7.rpy:1044
translate english chapter7_fee27d0b:

    # 나 "“저기, 잠깐―――”"
    나 "\"Wait a minute―――\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1048
translate english chapter7_42250a35:

    # "목소리가 닿지 않는지, 유미는 뒤를 돌아보지 않고 멀어져갔다. "
    "Either my voice didn't reach her or she chose not to hear it; Yumi didn't look back as she walked away."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1049
translate english chapter7_de53f5f2:

    # "무슨 이유에서 유미를 불렀던 건지는 정확히 알 수 없다. "
    "I couldn't exactly tell why I called out to Yumi."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1050
translate english chapter7_c712b7b0:

    # "그저 멈춰 세워야 할 것만 같아서라고 한다면, 그건 말도 안 되는 이유려나? "
    "If I said it was simply because I felt like I should stop her - would that be an absurd reason?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:1059
translate english chapter7_173a2d2c:

    # "일순간, 지금이 꿈만 같다는 느낌이 들었다. "
    "For a moment, I felt as if I were in a dream."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1061
translate english chapter7_aa307ba2:

    # "모든 것이 아득하게 느껴졌다. "
    "Everything seemed so distant."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1062
translate english chapter7_753c6011:

    # "폐전신국 앞에서 소녀가 사라졌을 때 받았던 그 감정을, 텅 빈 열차 안으로 발을 내디딜 때 느꼈던 그 감각을, 나는 다시금 마주하고 있었다. "
    "The feeling I had when the girl disappeared in front of the abandoned telegraph station, the sensation I felt when stepping into the empty train, I was facing them once again."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1068
translate english chapter7_1cc2f7e8:

    # "마치 꿈이 희미해지듯, 주변이 무너져갔다. "
    "As if a dream was fading away, my surroundings were crumbling."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1069
translate english chapter7_2007e5f3:

    # "멀어져가는 유미의 기척이 유리로 된 방음벽 너머에서 들려오는 외침처럼 느껴졌다. "
    "Yumi's receding presence felt like a scream from beyond a glass soundproof wall."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1073
translate english chapter7_5b761ae8:

    # "그 외침은 힘없이 타고 있던 성냥불처럼 덧없이 사그라들 뿐이었다. "
    "That scream faded away as futilely as a matchstick burning out."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1079
translate english chapter7_baa23bc1:

    # "정신을 차렸을 땐, 모든 것이 눈앞에서 눈처럼 녹아내린 것 같았다. "
    "When I came to my senses, everything seemed to have melted away before my eyes like snow."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1080
translate english chapter7_dd9b530b:

    # "인기척이 느껴지지 않는 대도시, 눈이 없는 망망한 설원이었다. "
    "A metropolis devoid of human presence, it was a vast snowfield without snow."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1081
translate english chapter7_305173b3:

    # "무인의 세계가, 또다시 연장선을 그린다. "
    "The world of solitude extended its line once again."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1082
translate english chapter7_2e63dbfb:

    # "어째서인지는 모르겠지만. "
    "I don't know why."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1087
translate english chapter7_396673fa_1:

    # 나 "“…….”"
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1091
translate english chapter7_1fde8b77:

    # "오른손을 움직이려다 말고, 나의 손을 잡고 있던 소녀와 눈이 마주쳤다. "
    "I stopped trying to move my right hand and locked eyes with the girl who had been holding it."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1092
translate english chapter7_2b949a6c:

    # "소녀는 나를 이상하다는 눈빛으로, 그리고 걱정스러운 눈빛으로 쳐다보고 있었다. "
    "The girl looked at me with a strange and worried expression."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1093
translate english chapter7_6d0b80dd:

    # "폐전신국 아래에서 보았던 것과, 똑같은 표정이었다. "
    "It was the same expression I had seen under the abandoned embassy."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1094
translate english chapter7_6e124b78:

    # "굳이 말을 꺼내지 않아도, ‘왜 그래요?’라고 걱정스레 묻는 듯한 그 표정 말이다. "
    "Without uttering a word, her face seemed to ask worryingly, 'What's wrong?'."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1101
translate english chapter7_152032a7:

    # 나 "“있잖아, 나 지금 꿈을 꾸는 걸까?”"
    나 "\"Hey, do you think I'm dreaming right now?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1106
translate english chapter7_c58bb36e:

    # voice "voices/gg65.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네에……?”"
    voice "voices/gg65.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Huh...?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1108
translate english chapter7_450d0548:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그리고 이게 만약 꿈이라면, 나는 언제부터 꿈을 꾸고 있었던 걸까?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"And if this is a dream, when did I start dreaming?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1119
translate english chapter7_bf8d8c20:

    # "꿈일 거라는 징조는 언제나 있었다. "
    "There were always signs that it could be a dream."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1120
translate english chapter7_45bc23c3:

    # "어제도, 그제도, 눈을 떴을 때의 모든 순간이 꿈이라 해도 전혀 이상할 건 없었으니까. "
    "Even yesterday and the day before that, it wouldn't have been strange at all if every moment when I woke up was a dream."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1124
translate english chapter7_8e58d9c4:

    # "모든 것이 사라진 뒤였다. "
    "Everything had disappeared."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1128
translate english chapter7_187bb289:

    # "지금이 꿈일 거라는 증거 하나만을, 덩그러니 남겨 둔 채. "
    "Leaving behind only one piece of evidence that this might be a dream."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1136
translate english chapter7_a8c770a1:

    # "하지만 어째서인지, 소녀는 자신이라는 불씨 하나만을 남겨 두고선 모조리 사그라들어버린 꿈만 같은 현실을 아무렇지도 않게 바라보고 있었다. "
    "I don't know why, But the girl stared at this reality that seemed like a dream that had completely collapsed. It looks like she is the only one who left here, like little ember buried in dark."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1138
translate english chapter7_03c0a2ff:

    # 나 "“…… 엄청 태연하네.”"
    나 "\"... You're incredibly calm.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1140
translate english chapter7_1c2034bb:

    # voice "voices/gg66.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“태연하다뇨……?”"
    voice "voices/gg66.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Calm...?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1142
translate english chapter7_0b42c5c5:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 정말 자신의 꿈을 이루는 조각이 되기라도 한 듯, 이방인을 보는 것 같은 시선으로 나를 쳐다보았다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl looked at me as if she herself had become a piece of a dream come true, with the gaze of a stranger."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1144
translate english chapter7_a06c6874:

    # "그런 소녀의 시선이, 정말 지금이 꿈일지도 모르겠다는 생각을 문득 들게 했다. "
    "Her gaze made me suddenly think that this might indeed be a dream."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1145
translate english chapter7_6d0f821a:

    # "잠시 후면 깨어나야 할, 길었던 꿈 말이다. "
    "A long dream from which I should wake up soon."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1147
translate english chapter7_4f7304db:

    # 나 "“…… 모두 사라졌잖아?”"
    나 "\"... Everything disappeared, didn't it?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1149
translate english chapter7_c6afe6fc:

    # "하지만 소녀는 내 말의 요지를 전혀 이해할 수 없다는 듯 고개를 갸웃거렸다. "
    "But the girl tilted her head as if she couldn't understand the point of my words at all."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1159
translate english chapter7_a055f922:

    # "유미도, 지나가던 사람들도, 주변의 모든 것이 감쪽같이 녹아내린 지금의 상황이 소녀에겐 전혀 이상하게 느껴지지 않는 것일까? "
    "Could it be that the current situation where Yumi, the passers-by, and everything around had completely melted away doesn't seem strange to the girl at all?"

# game/chapter7.rpy:1160
translate english chapter7_0d1988c3:

    # "나의 진지한 표정을, 그리고 주변의 텅 빈 풍경을, 난해한 틀린 그림 찾기 문제를 풀 때처럼 골똘히 살피던 소녀가, 도무지 모르겠다는 얼굴로 내게 다시 물었다. "
    "The girl who was scrutinizing my serious expression and the empty scenery around as if solving a difficult spot-the-difference puzzle asked me again with a puzzled face."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1167
translate english chapter7_789233db:

    # voice "voices/gg67.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“뭐가 사라졌다는 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gg67.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What do you mean 'disappeared'?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1170
translate english chapter7_45aab9f2:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀의 얼굴에도 장난기는 전혀 묻어있지 않았다. "
    voice ""
    "There was no playfulness on the girl's face at all."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1172
translate english chapter7_35b78ee5:

    # "소녀는 진지하기 그지없는 표정으로, 내게 난해한 틀린 그림 찾기 문제의 정답을 요구하고 있었다. "
    "With an utterly serious expression, the girl was demanding the answer to the baffling spot-the-difference puzzle from me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1174
translate english chapter7_265db9a6:

    # 나 "“유미도…….”"
    나 "\"Even Yumi...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1176
translate english chapter7_6307f437:

    # voice "voices/gg68.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그건 방금 건널목을 지나가서 그런 거잖아요.”"
    voice "voices/gg68.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's because you just crossed the railway crossing.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1178
translate english chapter7_9a48b04a:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“지나가던 사람들도 모두 사라졌잖아……?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"But all the passers-by have disappeared, haven't they...?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1181
translate english chapter7_f65af503:

    # voice "voices/gg69.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“무슨 소리예요, 지금 바로 앞에도 지나가고 있는걸요? 불그죽죽한 죽음의 색으로 그려진 두 사람이.”"
    voice "voices/gg69.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What are you talking about? Can't you see two people passing by right in front of us, painted in the flaming colors of death?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1184
translate english chapter7_85297318:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀의 시선이 허공을 훑는다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl's gaze sweeps through thin air."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1187
translate english chapter7_a7eb947a:

    # "그리고 나의 얼빠진 얼굴을 훑는다. "
    "And then it sweeps over my stunned face."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1190
translate english chapter7_2aa8fae1:

    # 나 "“그렇지만 내 눈엔…….”"
    나 "\"But in my eyes...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1192
translate english chapter7_07a5706b:

    # "말끝을 흐릴 수밖에 없었다. "
    "I had no choice but to trail off."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1198
translate english chapter7_9927ac83:

    # 나 "“아무도 안 보이는데…….”"
    나 "\"I can't see anyone...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1200
translate english chapter7_494fe3e8:

    # "소녀는 홀로 덩그러니 무인의 세계에 놓여버린 나를, 멍하니 바라보았다. "
    "The girl stared blankly at me, left alone in this deserted world."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1202
translate english chapter7_e3715655:

    # 나 "“일단 집으로 돌아가자. 일단은…….”"
    나 "\"Let's go home for now. At least for now...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1204
translate english chapter7_3950a343:

    # "도로에서는 호버크라프트들이 정적인 기계음을 내뿜으며 움직이기 시작했다. "
    "Hovercrafts on the road began to move with a static mechanical sound."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1205
translate english chapter7_9f7bc708:

    # "분명 몇 초 전까지만 해도 바쁜 유기체처럼 동작하던 주위의 모든 것들이, 지금은 생동감을 잃은 채 단순한 태엽장치처럼 굴러가고 있었다. "
    "Everything around that was bustling like an organic body just a few seconds ago was now rolling like a simple clockwork mechanism devoid of vitality."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1206
translate english chapter7_73b3b37b:

    # "적어도 나의 눈에는, 그렇게 보였다. "
    "At least in my eyes, it seemed that way."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1208
translate english chapter7_babef518:

    # voice "voices/gg70.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“갑자기 아무것도 안 보인다니, 그게 무슨 말이에요?”"
    voice "voices/gg70.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What do you mean you suddenly can't see anything?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1210
translate english chapter7_14f5b2ed:

    # voice ""
    # "불빛이 바뀐 횡단보도를 건너려는데, 다시 한번 소녀의 걱정 가득한 목소리가 들렸다. "
    voice ""
    "As I was about to cross the pedestrian crossing where the lights had changed, I heard the girl's voice filled with worry once again."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1213
translate english chapter7_d1c1f4e5:

    # 나 "“…… 말 그대로야. 눈앞에서 다른 사람들이 모두 사라졌―――”"
    나 "\"...Just as I said. Everyone else in front of me disappeared―――\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1215
translate english chapter7_2e8b599a:

    # "오른팔에서 느껴지는 인력에 당겨져, 소녀의 어깨와 맞닿는다. "
    "Pulled by a force from my right arm, I come into contact with the girl's shoulder."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1219
translate english chapter7_0dfbddcf:

    # voice "voices/gg71.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“부딪힐 뻔했어요.”"
    voice "voices/gg71.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You almost bumped into something.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1221
translate english chapter7_d1ce6ffa:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 이야기와 함께, 소녀는 한 발짝 앞서 나를 이끈 채 집으로 발걸음을 옮겼다. "
    voice ""
    "With that comment, the girl took a step ahead of me and began to lead me home."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1223
translate english chapter7_19aba81f:

    # "더는 말하지 않아도, 직접 확인하지 않아도 소녀는 대충 내 눈 앞에 펼쳐진 세계를 이해한 모양이었다. "
    "Even without saying more or verifying for herself, it seemed that the girl had roughly understood the world unfolding before my eyes."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1225
translate english chapter7_455b80c9:

    # "아니, 어쩌면 소녀는 이미 그런 세계를 알고 있었던 건지도 모르겠다. "
    "No, perhaps she already knew about such a world."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1235
translate english chapter7_94ee63df:

    # "낮이 점점 짧아지고 있었다. "
    "The days were getting shorter."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1236
translate english chapter7_871a65b2:

    # "여름의 흔적이라고는 이젠 가벼운 복장만이 남아, 새로운 계절의 도래를 기다리고 있었다. "
    "Only light clothing remained as a trace of summer, waiting for the arrival of a new season."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1237
translate english chapter7_cd753feb:

    # "물론 소녀의 가벼운 복장은 여름이 끝나더라도 변함없이, 어떤 여름의 날에 머물러 있겠지만. "
    "Of course, even after summer ends, the girl's light attire would remain unchanged as if stuck on some summer day."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1239
translate english chapter7_eaf4115f:

    # "베란다의 난간에 기대어 창밖을 바라보았지만, 거리는 여전히 생동감 없이 돌아갈 뿐이었다. "
    "Leaning against the balustrade of the veranda, I looked out of the window, but the street was still devoid of life, just spinning around."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1240
translate english chapter7_e8d4efd0:

    # "어둠이 깔리고, 밤이 깊어갔다. "
    "Darkness fell, and the night deepened."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1241
translate english chapter7_659057d5:

    # "나의 눈에 비친 동력을 잃은 세상. "
    "The world reflected in my eyes had lost its momentum."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1243
translate english chapter7_05cb36eb:

    # "그리고 동력을 잃어버린 건 내 눈에 비친 풍경만이 아니었다. "
    "And it wasn't just the landscape reflected in my eyes that had lost its momentum."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1248
translate english chapter7_f3c1299f:

    # voice "voices/gg72.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이제 바람이 시원해졌네요.”"
    voice "voices/gg72.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The wind is now cool.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1250
translate english chapter7_085c8575_1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그러게.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Seems so.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1253
translate english chapter7_3a710bee:

    # "어느새 한 손에 머그잔을 들고 곁에 다가온 소녀가, 난간에 함께 팔을 얹으며 말을 걸어왔다. "
    "The girl who had come to my side with a mug in one hand started a conversation as she leaned her arm on the balustrade with me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1255
translate english chapter7_8f06680a:

    # voice "voices/gg73.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“바보 같은 짓이었죠? 떨어지는 저를 받으려는 것도, 직접 그 높은 곳에서 떨어지겠다고 말한 것도?”"
    voice "voices/gg73.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It was foolish, wasn't it? Trying to catch me when I was falling and saying you'd jump from that high place yourself?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1257
translate english chapter7_085c8575_2:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그러게.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Seems so.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1260
translate english chapter7_c1985308:

    # voice "voices/gg74.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이젠, 어떻게 할 생각인가요?”"
    voice "voices/gg74.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What are you going to do now?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1262
translate english chapter7_959327df_1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 글쎄.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...I don't know.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1265
translate english chapter7_9e609b77:

    # "동력을 거의 다 상실한 무기력한 목소리가, 목에서 흘러나왔다. "
    "A voice almost devoid of vitality slipped from my throat."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1266
translate english chapter7_38a156a8:

    # "침묵이 길어져 혹시나 하고 옆을 돌아본 곳에서는, 소녀가 조용히 그 자리를 지키고 있었다. "
    "As the silence stretched on, I turned to look at her, and there she was, quietly holding her place."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1268
translate english chapter7_d8aa39c3:

    # voice "voices/gg75.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“요 며칠 동안 여기저기 돌아다니느라 피곤했을 텐데, 늦었으니까 지금이라도 자는 게 어떨까요? 그러면 뭔가 할 수 있는 일이 떠오를지도 모르고요.”"
    voice "voices/gg75.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You must have been tired from running around these past few days. How about you get some sleep now? You might come up with something you can do.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1274
translate english chapter7_2a60d908:

    # voice ""
    # "머뭇대며 내게 수면을 권하는 소녀. "
    voice ""
    "The girl who hesitated as she suggested that I sleep."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1276
translate english chapter7_977aada2:

    # "나는 눈을 지그시 감고선 잔상으로 남은 소녀의 모습을 붙잡아 보았다. "
    "I gently closed my eyes and tried to hold onto the image of the girl that remained as an afterimage."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1277
translate english chapter7_1e5d9172:

    # "애써 붙잡아 보려 했던 소녀의 형체는, 얼마 안 가 흐릿하게 흩어져버렸다. "
    "The figure of the girl that I desperately tried to hold onto soon blurred and dispersed."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1279
translate english chapter7_bbcc78e6:

    # 나 "“있지, 나 말이야. 가끔 이런 꿈을 꿨었어.”"
    나 "\"You know, I've had dreams like this sometimes.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1281
translate english chapter7_175da8bb:

    # "슬그머니 눈을 떠, 소녀의 모습을 다시금 눈동자에 새긴다. "
    "Slowly opening my eyes, I etched the image of the girl back into my pupils."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1285
translate english chapter7_d8388cb6:

    # 나 "“눈을 떠 보니 모든 것이 사라지고 있는 꿈. 그런데 말이야, 누가 뭐래도 비현실적인 상황인데, 그게 꿈이라는 생각은 전혀 안 들더라고.”"
    나 "\"In the dream, everything disappears when I open my eyes. But you know what? Even though it's an unrealistic situation, I never think that it's a dream.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1287
translate english chapter7_1b100c30:

    # "그리고는 다시 눈을 감았다. "
    "And then I closed my eyes again."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1288
translate english chapter7_aa5bb056:

    # "소녀의 잔상은 아주 조금 더 눈동자에 머무르다 서서히 흩어져갔다. "
    "The afterimage of the girl lingered in my pupils just a little longer before slowly dispersing."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1292
translate english chapter7_7866b3b1:

    # 나 "“그런 꿈을 꾸고 일어나면, 그날 하루는 계속 꿈을 걷는 기분이었어. 아니, 어쩌면 이 모든 순간이 내가 꾸고 있는 속절없이 긴 꿈일 거라고도 생각했고.”"
    나 "\"When I wake up from such a dream, it feels like I'm walking in a dream all day. No, maybe I thought that all these moments are part of a long dream that I'm having.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1294
translate english chapter7_83dff5f7:

    # "흐려진 잔상은 소녀의 모습을 더는 간직하고 있지 않았다. "
    "The blurred afterimage no longer held the figure of the girl."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1295
translate english chapter7_8474e6e7:

    # "그저 소녀의 차가우면서도 따뜻한 역설적인 감각만이 어렴풋이 남아 흔적을 마련할 뿐. "
    "Only the paradoxically cold yet warm sensation of the girl vaguely remained, leaving a trace."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1301
translate english chapter7_21918094:

    # 나 "“그래서 말이야, 나는 현실에서 그런 일이 일어나도 꿈에서처럼 태연할 수 있을 줄 알았어. 꿈에서는…… 그런 일이 일어나도 언제나 태연했거든.”"
    나 "\"So, I thought I could be calm in reality as I am in my dreams when such things happen. In dreams... I was always calm no matter what happened.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1303
translate english chapter7_296e685b:

    # voice "voices/gg76.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럴 리가 없잖아요. 현실은 현실이고, 꿈은 꿈인걸요.”"
    voice "voices/gg76.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's impossible. Reality is reality, and dreams are dreams.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1306
translate english chapter7_9a1028fb:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그럼 지금이 꿈이 아니라고, 내 볼을 한 번만 꼬집어 줄 수 있어?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Then can you pinch my cheek once to prove this isn't a dream?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1309
translate english chapter7_c40eebed:

    # voice "voices/gg77.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 뭔가요, 그런 부탁은.”"
    voice "voices/gg77.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... What a strange request.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1311
translate english chapter7_1596bf07:

    # voice ""
    # "볼멘소리를 하면서도, 소녀는 나의 뺨을 쿡 꼬집어 주었다. "
    voice ""
    "Despite her complaints, the girl pinched my cheek."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1313
translate english chapter7_81bf8e78:

    # "볼에 닿는 따끔한 감각에, 나의 눈이 뜨였다. "
    "At the stinging sensation on my cheek, I opened my eyes."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1315
translate english chapter7_c3f4217b:

    # 나 "“아야…….”"
    나 "\"Ouch...\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1317
translate english chapter7_60e44276:

    # voice "voices/gg78.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“됐어요?”"
    voice "voices/gg78.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Are you satisfied now?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1319
translate english chapter7_c5bcf6ec:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 충분한 것 같아.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... I think that's enough.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1322
translate english chapter7_0ddf077c:

    # "볼 위의 따끔따끔한 감각이, 왠지 기분 좋은 텔레파시 신호 같이 느껴졌다. "
    "The prickling sensation on my cheek felt somewhat like a pleasant telepathic signal."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1323
translate english chapter7_99200056:

    # "머그잔의 차를 한 모금 마신 소녀가 난간에서 손을 떼고는 등을 기대었다. "
    "The girl who had taken a sip of tea from the mug removed her hand from the balustrade and leaned back."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1327
translate english chapter7_b7012a8b:

    # 나 "“실은 오늘 낮에, 폐전신국 아래에서 아무것도 아니었다고 말한 건 거짓말이었어.”"
    나 "\"Actually, when I said it was nothing under the abandoned telegraph station today, I was lying.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1329
translate english chapter7_b1e0fe4e:

    # voice "voices/gg79.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“거짓말은 나쁜 거예요.”"
    voice "voices/gg79.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Lying is not good.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1331
translate english chapter7_667ecb57:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 말을 하고선, 소녀는 태연히 머그잔을 마저 비웠다. "
    voice ""
    "After saying that, the girl calmly finished her mug."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1334
translate english chapter7_7982f5c9:

    # 나 "“기억나? 거기서 내가 얼빠진 표정 지었던 거.”"
    나 "\"Do you remember? My dumbfounded expression there.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1336
translate english chapter7_ff2d1056:

    # voice "voices/gg80.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“기억나요. 그때 몇 번을 불렀는데 대답이 없어서 얼마나 이상하게 생각했는데요.”"
    voice "voices/gg80.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I remember. I called you several times then and you didn't answer. I thought it was strange.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1338
translate english chapter7_51d08fd1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“네 목소리도, 기척도, 아무것도 느껴지지 않았거든. 떨어지는 너를 받고 나서, 네가 사라진 줄로만 알았어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I couldn't feel your voice or presence at all. After catching you falling, I thought you had disappeared.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1341
translate english chapter7_13944a5c:

    # voice "voices/gg81.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“제가 보이지 않았다는 건가요.”"
    voice "voices/gg81.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You mean you couldn't see me?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1343
translate english chapter7_c1fbfe1b:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“맞아. 하지만 그때는 네가 말 그대로 사라져버렸다고만 생각했거든. 그래서 그런 멍청한 표정을 지은 채 굳어있었는데, 다시 네가 내 눈앞에 나타난 거야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Right. But at that time, I just thought you had literally disappeared. That's why I was frozen with such a stupid expression on my face when you reappeared before my eyes.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1346
translate english chapter7_35790796:

    # "여름의 밤, 가느다란 바람 줄기가 둘을 훑고 지나갔다. "
    "On this summer night, a thin stream of wind swept past them."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1347
translate english chapter7_c4d8a8ac:

    # "소녀의 말대로 온기가 거의 느껴지지 않는 바람이었다. "
    "Just as the girl said, it was a wind that barely felt warm."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1349
translate english chapter7_a6b0ad21:

    # 나 "“사라지지 않은 너를 마주하고 나서, 내가 뭐라고 생각했는지 알아?”"
    나 "\"Do you know what I thought after facing you who hadn't disappeared?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1351
translate english chapter7_3e44f4b2:

    # "난간에 얹은 양팔 속으로 얼굴을 파묻어, 달빛을 등졌다. "
    "Burying his face in his arms resting on the balustrade, he turned his back to the moonlight."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1353
translate english chapter7_e55a5709:

    # 나 "“다행이라고 생각했어. 네가 사라지지 않아서 다행이다…… 라고 말이야. 어이없지?”"
    나 "\"I thought it was a relief. I mean, it's a relief that you didn't disappear... Ridiculous, isn't it?\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1354
translate english chapter7_de67a983:

    # "속으로 자조 섞인 웃음을 삼켰다. "
    "He swallowed a self-mocking laugh within."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1355
translate english chapter7_13bdb554:

    # "침묵이 다가올 거라고만 생각했다. "
    "He had only expected silence to follow."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1356
translate english chapter7_1aa83e8f:

    # "그랬기에, 귓가로 속삭이듯 들려온 소녀의 목소리는 정말 의외였다. "
    "Therefore, the girl's voice whispering in his ear was truly unexpected."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1360
translate english chapter7_57e0fbf3:

    # voice "voices/gg82.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“다행이네요.”"
    voice "voices/gg82.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's fortunate.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1362
translate english chapter7_feb1a962:

    # voice ""
    # "고개를 아주 살짝 들어, 한쪽 눈으로 소녀를 바라보았다. "
    voice ""
    "He slightly lifted his head and looked at the girl with one eye."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1364
translate english chapter7_445e5458:

    # "소녀는 내 쪽으로 어느새 가까이 다가와, 고개를 파묻고 있던 나를 쓰다듬어 주듯 내려보고 있었다. "
    "The girl had quietly approached him and was looking down at him as if to comfort him, his head buried in his arms."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1366
translate english chapter7_350f1b80:

    # voice "voices/gg83.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“다행이에요. 다행이라고 생각할 수 있게 되어서요.”"
    voice "voices/gg83.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's fortunate. That you're able to think it's a relief.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1373
translate english chapter7_1dc91f3e:

    # voice ""
    # "웃으며 그렇게 이야기한 소녀가 고개를 들어 시선을 위로 향했다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl who spoke with a smile lifted her gaze upwards."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1375
translate english chapter7_ec30626b:

    # "소녀를 따라, 나 역시 고개를 들어 밤하늘의 한 편을 바라보았다. "
    "Following the girl's gaze, he too looked up at a piece of the night sky."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1376
translate english chapter7_0b10b116:

    # "희미한 별빛 몇 조각과 달빛만이 외롭게 하늘에서 반짝였다. "
    "Only a few faint stars and the moonlight were lonely twinkling in the sky."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1378
translate english chapter7_7d6d6be3:

    # voice "voices/gg84.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“저희, 같은 곳을 보고 있어요.”"
    voice "voices/gg84.ogg"
    소녀 "\"We're looking at the same place.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1381
translate english chapter7_030e45d5:

    # voice ""
    # "그 말 한마디에 기대어, 나는 잠시 소녀와 단 둘뿐인 순간을 만끽했다. "
    voice ""
    "Leaning on her words, I savored the moment that was just the two of us, the girl and me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1383
translate english chapter7_60b5c193:

    # "지금 이 순간을, 그리고 여태껏 서로에게 기대왔던 그 순간들을. "
    "This moment, and all those moments we've been relying on each other until now."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1411
translate english chapter7_c829bb0a:

    # narl "모조리, 모조리 끌어모아 지금의 감각에 흩뿌린다. "
    narl "I gather them all, all of them, and scatter them into my current senses."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1412
translate english chapter7_39782936:

    # narl "오랫동안, 오랫동안, 기억 속에 간직할 수 있도록……. "
    narl "For a long time, for a long time, so that I can keep it in my memory..."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1423
translate english chapter7_af127315:

    # "베란다 문을 닫고선 소녀를 따라 침대에 기대어 앉았지만, 여전히 잠은 오지 않았다. "
    "After closing the veranda door, I leaned on the bed following the girl, but sleep still didn't come."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1424
translate english chapter7_14e623fe:

    # "흐릿한 불빛 아래에 앉아 눈만 멀뚱거리는 나에게, 소녀는 의아한 눈길을 보냈다. "
    "Sitting under the dim light and just blankly staring with my eyes, the girl sent me a curious glance."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1425
translate english chapter7_d76b906f:

    # "정확히 이야기하자면, 잠이 오지 않는다기보다는―――"
    "To be precise, it's not that sleep doesn't come—"

# game/chapter7.rpy:1427
translate english chapter7_f15f3850:

    # 나 "“…… 무서워서 그래. 잠들기 무서워서.”"
    나 "\"... I'm scared. Scared to fall asleep.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1429
translate english chapter7_91b75b83:

    # "흐릿한 수면 유도등 아래에 기대어 앉아, 나는 옆에 함께 앉은 소녀에게 작은 목소리로 중얼거렸다. "
    "Leaning under the dim sleep-inducing light, I mumbled in a small voice to the girl sitting next to me."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1431
translate english chapter7_5d21bfe5:

    # 나 "“이렇게 잠들어 버리면 다시 그 꿈을 꾸게 될까 봐. 그리고 눈을 떴을 땐, 정말 그 꿈처럼 눈앞에 아무도 없을까 봐――― 아얏.”"
    나 "\"If I fall asleep like this, I might dream that dream again. And when I open my eyes... there might really be no one in front of me like in that dream— Ow.\""

# game/chapter7.rpy:1433
translate english chapter7_623e1fa5:

