# game/chapter7.rpy:1462
translate english chapter7_48bbdf57:

    # "소녀가 허밍을 읊조렸다. "
    "The girl hummed a tune."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1463
translate english chapter7_637faae2:

    # "익숙한 선율이었다. "
    "It was a familiar melody."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1464
translate english chapter7_5ec5f2d9:

    # "모를 리가 없는 울림이었다. "
    "It was a resonance that was impossible not to recognize."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1465
translate english chapter7_2cc1ba37:

    # "하지만 내가 연주했을 땐 그저 서툴게만 느껴졌던 그 음정들은, 소녀에 의해 더할 나위 없이 완벽하게 정돈되어 흘러나오고 있었다. "
    "The notes that had seemed merely clumsy when I played them were now flowing out impeccably arranged by the girl."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1466
translate english chapter7_b8791f2d:

    # "마치, 원래 자신의 곡이었다는 것처럼 말이다. "
    "As if it were originally her own song."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1467
translate english chapter7_9fc4877e:

    # "나의 심장이 선율에 맞추어 공명하기 시작했다. "
    "My heart began to resonate in tune with the melody."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1468
translate english chapter7_e112bd0d:

    # "그리고 거짓말처럼, 이런 상황을 바라기라도 한 것처럼. "
    "And as if by a lie, as if I had been hoping for such a situation."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1469
translate english chapter7_333c4c90:

    # "기억 속에서 목소리가 선을 이루며 들려왔다. "
    "Voices formed lines in my memory and echoed in my ears."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1473
translate english chapter7_eeaaf325:

    # "목소리가 들려올 때마다 펼쳐지던 여름날의 기억도 어느새 끝을 향해 달려가고 있었다. "
    "With each voice that echoed, the memories of summer days unfolded and were now racing towards an end."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1474
translate english chapter7_7bc40f27:

    # "치열하던 대회도, 타오르던 더위도, 이제 마지막 페이지가 얼마 남지 않아 보였다. "
    "The fierce competition, the burning heat, it seemed there weren't many pages left now."

# game/chapter7.rpy:1475
translate english chapter7_e86e1abf:

    # "어쩌면 이것이 내 마지막 기억일 수도 있음을 직감하며, 그날의 일을 떠올렸다. "
    "Maybe sensing this could be my last memory, I recalled the events of that day."

